ft=3Dtrue" rel=3D""><span>Give a gift subscription</span></a></p><p><span>B=
elow is a transcript, lightly edited, with some highlights from </span><a h=
ref=3D"https://youtu.be/iKgbkLcauDM" rel=3D"">my discussion at Wellesley Co=
llege</a><span>. We spoke about authenticity, elite hypocrisy, social mobil=
